All Implemented Interfaces:
IDeployAttributeValidator
public class DeployAttributeNotNullValidator
extends DeployAttributeValidator

Validates that an attribute of e deploy model object is not null.

To validate the existance of a non-null RequirementExpression use DeployRequirementAttributeNotNullValidator.

To validate a string as non-null and of non-zero length use DeployAttributeStringNotEmptyValidator.
